stabilizes the situation.

488
00:29:11.458 --> 00:29:12.752
You're depending
on the government?

489
00:29:12.877 --> 00:29:13.920
I'm not depending on anyone.

490
00:29:14.045 --> 00:29:15.297
I'm just making a bet
that the government's

491
00:29:15.422 --> 00:29:17.423
